
@1071 = ~Longsword~
@1072 = ~The Memory of the Myths +5~
@1073 = ~This blade once belonged to Telva, an elven knight who devoted her life to hunting the undead. Legends say it shattered in battle against a dracolich, yet its holy purpose endured — the steel dissolving into a spectral edge shaped by Telva’s final stand. Since that day, the weapon cannot harm the living, but its power against the undead has only grown, striking both decaying flesh and incorporeal forms with unwavering clarity.

STATISTICS:

Combat abilities:
– Can only harm undead creatures
– Does not receive bonus damage from Strength
– Critical hits do not deal bonus damage
– 20% chance on hit to deal 2d8+5 additional fire damage to undead (Save vs. Spells at –5 to halve)
– 10% chance on hit to instantly destroy undead target

THAC0: +5
Damage: 2d8+5 (magic, vs. undead only)
Speed Factor: 3
Proficiency Type: Long Sword
Type: One-handed
Requires:
 6 Strength

Weight: 2
~

@1081 = ~Robe~
@1082 = ~The Undyings's Slumber~
@1083 = ~This ancient robe, known as The Undying’s Slumber, is said to have once adorned the form of the Undying himself — a fallen archmage of Myth Unnohyr. Once a garment of the High Art, it now bears the faint taint of unlife and decay. Its fabric shimmers like a robe of the archmagi, yet the weave is warped, as if time itself recoiled from its touch. Despite its dark history, the robe still hums with quiet power, eager to serve another who dares to wield what remains of the elven High Magic. 

STATISTICS:

Charge abilities:
– May cast Vampiric Touch once per day
– May cast Greater Malison once per day

Equipped abilities:
– Armor Class: 5
– Magic Resistance: +5%
– Caster level (arcane): +1

Weight: 6
~

@1095 = ~Create Mystic Candle (Mage)~
@1096 = ~Create Mystic Candle (Level 5) has been added to your priest spellbook.~
@1097 = ~Create Mystic Candle (Level 5) has been added to your mage spellbook.~
@1098 = ~Create Mystic Candle (Priest)~
@1099 = ~Create Mystic Candle
(Evocation)

Level: 5
Range: 0
Duration: 24 hours
Casting Time: 8
Area of Effect: The caster
Saving Throw: None

This spell allows the caster to create a Mystic Candle capable of holding a special enchantment, which may be triggered when the candle is used. The caster can channel magical power and certain ingredients into the candle, storing the spell for later use. Each color of candle produces a different effect:

Red - Charm Person or Mammal
Blue - Protection from Evil, 10' radius
Purple - Know Alignment  
Gold - Cure Medium Wounds
Yellow - Command
Green - Luck
White - Neutralize Poison
Silver - Draw Upon Holy Might
Black - Doom

The candle may be used by the caster or another character, provided they have at least 12 or more Wisdom. After twenty four hours passes, the candle is destroyed.~
@1100 = ~Create Mystic Candle
(Evocation)

Level: 5
Range: 0
Duration: 24 hours
Casting Time: 8
Area of Effect: The caster
Saving Throw: None

This spell allows the caster to create a Mystic Candle capable of holding a special enchantment, which may be triggered when the candle is used. The caster can channel magical power and certain ingredients into the candle, storing the spell for later use. Each color of candle produces a different effect:

Red - Charm Person or Mammal (up to 3 targets)
Blue - Protection from Evil, 10' radius
Purple - Know Alignment (up to 3 targets)
Gold - Cure Medium Wounds
Yellow - Command (up to 3 targets)
Green - Luck (up to 3 targets)
White - Neutralize Poison
Silver - Draw Upon Holy Might
Black - Doom (up to 3 targets)

The candle may be used by the caster or another character, provided they have at least 12 or more Wisdom. After twenty four hours passes, the candle is destroyed.
~
